text: Kate Thill (born 25 January 2002) is a Luxembourger footballer who plays as a forward for Dames Ligue 1 club SC Bettembourg and the Luxembourg women's national team. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers
